- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science): The paper discusses proof trees and formalizing domain reduction, which are relevant to logic in computer science. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper discusses search trees and operators for local consistency notions, which are relevant to data structures and algorithms.
